## Contratos Compartilhados

Estes contratos definem as interfaces que TODOS os tracks usam. Cada agente implementa apenas seus arquivos mas DEVE respeitar esses tipos.

### Enums Prisma (owner: Renato T1 — `prisma/schema.prisma`)

```prisma
enum NotificationType {
  TASK_OVERDUE
  TASK_DUE_SOON
  MESSAGE
  MENTION
  SYSTEM
}

enum NotificationStatus {
  UNREAD
  READ
  CLEARED
  SNOOZED
}

enum NotificationCategory {
  PRIMARY
  OTHER
}
```

### Model Prisma (owner: Renato T1 — `prisma/schema.prisma`)

```prisma
model Notification {
  id           String               @id @default(cuid())
  createdAt    DateTime             @default(now()) @map("created_at")
  updatedAt    DateTime             @updatedAt @map("updated_at")
  deletedAt    DateTime?            @map("deleted_at")

  userId       String               @map("user_id")
  user         User                 @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  type         NotificationType
  category     NotificationCategory
  title        String
  description  String
  entityId     String?              @map("entity_id")
  entityUrl    String?              @map("entity_url")
  status       NotificationStatus   @default(UNREAD)
  snoozedUntil DateTime?            @map("snoozed_until")
  readAt       DateTime?            @map("read_at")
  clearedAt    DateTime?            @map("cleared_at")

  @@index([userId, status, createdAt], name: "idx_notifications_user_status_created")
  @@index([userId, category, status], name: "idx_notifications_user_category_status")
  @@index([userId, status], name: "idx_notifications_user_status")
  @@index([snoozedUntil], name: "idx_notifications_snoozed_until")
  @@map("notifications")
}
```

